%% Diagram: Trip State Machine
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> REQUESTED: POST /rides
    REQUESTED --> MATCHED: DISCO assigns driver
    REQUESTED --> CANCELLED: rider cancels<br/>or no supply
    MATCHED --> DRIVER_ARRIVING: driver accepts
    MATCHED --> CANCELLED: driver declines<br/>(reassign)
    DRIVER_ARRIVING --> DRIVER_ARRIVED: ETA < 60s<br/>or geofence hit
    DRIVER_ARRIVED --> IN_PROGRESS: rider boards<br/>(driver taps Start)
    DRIVER_ARRIVED --> CANCELLED: no-show<br/>(fee applies)
    IN_PROGRESS --> COMPLETED: driver taps End<br/>charge fires
    COMPLETED --> [*]
    CANCELLED --> [*]
